Package: ALTIS
Title: R Package for the analysis of large-scale TraDIS infection screens with Stan
Version: 0.0
Authors@R: person("Laura", "Jenniches", email = "laura.jenniches@helmholtz-hiri.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Analyse TraDIS data with
    multivariate models using the statistical modeling language Stan. Stan models are in the
    directory stan_models, scripts to reproduce the analysis of a Shigella TraDIS infection screens
    are in the directory scripts.
Depends: R (>= 4.3.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
